# Bonyad App - User Guide Documentation for RAG System

This document provides comprehensive information about the Bonyad app features, navigation, and user flows. It is structured for RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) systems to help users via chatbot assistance.

---

## Table of Contents

1. [App Overview](#app-overview)
2. [User Roles](#user-roles)
3. [Main Navigation](#main-navigation)
4. [User Features](#user-features)
5. [Service Provider Features](#service-provider-features)
6. [Common Tasks](#common-tasks)
7. [Settings and Preferences](#settings-and-preferences)
8. [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)

---

## App Overview

Bonyad is a construction services platform that connects property owners with service providers (technicians) for various construction and maintenance projects.

### Key Capabilities
- *Project Management*: Create, track, and manage construction projects
- *Service Provider Discovery*: Browse and select technicians by service category
- *Appointment Scheduling*: Book and manage appointments with service providers
- *Bidding System*: Service providers can bid on available projects
- *Contract Management*: Digital contract signing and phase-based project execution
- *Portfolio Management*: Service providers can create and manage their professional portfolios
- *Real-time Chat*: Communicate with service providers or users
- *Notifications*: Stay updated on project status, bids, and appointments

---

## User Roles

### Regular User (Property Owner)
- Can create projects (manually or using AI)
- Can browse service providers by category
- Can book appointments
- Can view project status and timeline
- Can approve phases and sign contracts
- Can make payments for project phases

### Service Provider (Technician)
- Can view available projects to bid on
- Can submit bids for projects
- Can manage portfolio and past projects
- Can view assigned projects
- Can complete project phases
- Can manage appointments
- Can view commission payments

---

## Main Navigation

### User Home Screen (HomeView)
*Location*: Main tab bar - Home icon (center circular button)

*Features*:
- *Header*: Logo on left, notification bell and chat icon on right (always LTR layout)
- *Search Bar*: Search for services or service providers
- *Service Providers Section*: Horizontal scrollable row showing all available services
  - Each service card navigates to ServiceProvidersView showing technicians for that service
  - "All services" button navigates to PickServiceView for all services
- *My Projects List*: Shows user's projects with status filters
- *Floating Chatbot Button*: Access AI assistant help

*Tab Bar (Bottom)*:
- *Profile* (left)
- *New Project* (+) (center-left)
- *Home* (center - circular button)
- *My Projects* (right)
- *Appointments* (right)

### Service Provider Home Screen (HomeService)
*Location*: Main tab bar - Home icon (center)

*Features*:
- *Header*: Logo on left, notification bell and chat icon on right (always LTR layout)
- *Create Portfolio Button*: Purple button to create professional portfolio (shown if no portfolio exists)
- *Available Projects*: List of projects available to bid on
- *Assigned Projects*: Projects assigned to the technician
- *Action Buttons* (2x2 grid):
  - *Look for Offers*: Browse available projects
  - *Direct Offers*: View direct offers
  - *My Offers*: View submitted offers
  - *Bidded Projects*: View projects where bids were placed

*Tab Bar (Bottom)*:
- *Projects* (left)
- *Appointments* (left-center)
- *Home* (center)
- *Payments* (right-center)
- *Profile* (right)

---

## User Features

### Creating a Project

*Path*: Home tab → "+" button → Choose creation method

*Two Methods*:
1. *AI-Assisted Creation*:
   - Tap "Using AI" option
   - Describe your project in natural language
   - AI generates project details, phases, and budget estimates
   - Review and edit AI suggestions
   - Submit project

2. *Manual Creation*:
   - Tap "Manually" option
   - Fill out project form:
     - Project title and description
     - Category selection
     - Address/location
     - Budget
     - Duration
     - Phases (add multiple phases)
   - Upload photos
   - Submit project

*After Creation*:
- Project appears in "My Projects" tab
- Status timeline shows: Creating → Pending → Bid Received → Approved → Contract
- Can edit project details
- Can add/remove phases
- Can upload additional photos

### Browsing Service Providers

*Path*: Home tab → Service Providers section

*Options*:
1. *By Category*: Tap any service card to see technicians for that service
2. *View All*: Tap "All services" to see all available services in a grid
3. *Search*: Use search bar to find specific services or providers

*Service Provider Cards Show*:
- Service category icon and color
- Service name
- Fixed size: 170x150 pixels

### Viewing Projects

*Path*: My Projects tab (or Home → My Projects section)

*Features*:
- *Status Filters*: All, Pending, Active, Completed
- *2-Column Grid*: Projects displayed in cards
- *Project Card Shows*:
  - Project title
  - Budget (with SAR icon)
  - Status badge
- *Tap Project*: Navigates to ProjectStatusTimelineView showing:
  - Project timeline with status indicators
  - Phase details
  - Budget breakdown
  - Edit options
  - Contract signing (when applicable)

### Managing Appointments

*Path*: Appointments tab

*Features*:
- *Calendar Widget*: Shows current month, select dates
- *Filter Tabs*: Today, Pending, Upcoming, Completed
- *Appointment Cards Show*:
  - Project description
  - Date and time
  - Address
  - Status
  - Total amount
- *Actions*: View details, reschedule, cancel

### Project Status Timeline

*Path*: My Projects → Tap any project

*Timeline Statuses*:
1. *Creating*: Project being created (+ icon)
2. *Pending*: Waiting for bids
3. *Bid Received*: Bids available for review
4. *Approved*: Project approved, contract ready
5. *Contract*: Contract signed, work in progress

*Actions Available*:
- Edit project details
- Add/remove phases
- Upload photos
- Approve phases
- Sign contract
- Make payments
- View bids (if applicable)

---

## Service Provider Features

### Creating Portfolio

*Path*: Home tab → "Create Portfolio" button (purple button)

*Steps*:
1. Tap "Create Portfolio" button
2. View benefits and information
3. Tap "Create Portfolio" to proceed
4. Fill out portfolio information:
   - Bio/description
   - Years of experience
   - Certificates (upload photos)
   - Select regions of service
5. Submit portfolio
6. Wait for admin approval

*After Approval*:
- Portfolio becomes public
- Can generate PDF portfolio
- Can add past projects
- Can edit portfolio details

### Bidding on Projects

*Path*: Home tab → Available Projects → Tap project → "Bid Now"

*Bidding Process*:
1. View project details
2. Review phases and requirements
3. Tap "Bid Now" button
4. Fill bid form:
   - Price per phase
   - Total price
   - Estimated duration
   - Notes/comments
5. Submit bid

*Bid Status*:
- *Pending*: Waiting for user review
- *Accepted*: Project assigned to you
- *Rejected*: Bid not selected

### Managing Assigned Projects

*Path*: Home tab → Assigned Projects section

*Features*:
- View all projects assigned to you
- See project status and timeline
- Complete phases (only after payment received)
- Request visit appointments
- Upload progress photos
- Submit phase completion

*Phase Completion Rules*:
- Phase can only be completed if payment received
- "Complete Phase" button hidden after completion
- Status updates automatically

### Viewing Available Projects

*Path*: Projects tab (or Home → Available Projects → "View All")

*Features*:
- *2-Column Grid*: All available projects
- *Project Cards Show*:
  - Project title
  - Category
  - Budget
  - Status
  - Distance (if location enabled)
- *Filter Options*: By status, category
- *Search*: Search projects by keywords

*Actions*:
- Tap project to view details
- Submit bid
- Request visit appointment

### Managing Appointments

*Path*: Appointments tab

*Features*:
- *Calendar View*: Select dates
- *Filter Tabs*: Today, Pending, Upcoming, Completed
- *Appointment Cards*: Show project, date, time, address
- *Actions*: Mark as completed, view details

### Portfolio Management

*Path*: Profile tab → My Portfolio

*Features*:
- *Profile Card*: Shows technician name and "Public Portfolio" status
- *Portfolio Section*:
  - Generate PDF portfolio
  - Download PDF
  - View QR code for portfolio
- *Past Projects Section*:
  - Add new past project
  - Edit existing projects
  - Delete projects
  - Upload project photos

---

## Common Tasks

### How to Create a New Project

1. Open app and go to Home tab
2. Tap the "+" button in the bottom tab bar (center-left)
3. Choose creation method:
   - *AI*: Describe your project, AI will generate details
   - *Manual*: Fill out form yourself
4. Complete required fields (title, description, address, budget, phases)
5. Upload photos (optional)
6. Tap "Submit" or "Create Project"
7. Project appears in "My Projects" tab

### How to Find a Service Provider

1. Go to Home tab
2. Scroll to "Service Providers" section
3. *Option A*: Tap any service card to see technicians for that service
4. *Option B*: Tap "All services" to browse all services
5. *Option C*: Use search bar to search for specific services
6. Tap on a service provider to view their profile
7. Book appointment or contact via chat

### How to Book an Appointment

1. Navigate to a service provider's profile
2. Tap "Book Appointment" button
3. Select date and time
4. Enter project details (if applicable)
5. Confirm appointment
6. Appointment appears in "Appointments" tab

### How to View Project Status

1. Go to "My Projects" tab
2. Select a project from the list
3. View timeline showing current status
4. See all phases and their completion status
5. View budget breakdown
6. Access actions: Edit, Add Address, Upload Photos, Approve Phases

### How to Approve a Bid

1. Go to "My Projects" tab
2. Select project with "Bid Received" status
3. View all bids from service providers
4. Review bid details (price, duration, notes)
5. Tap "Accept" on desired bid
6. Project status changes to "Approved"
7. Contract becomes available for signing

### How to Sign Contract

1. Go to project with "Approved" status
2. Tap "Sign Contract" button
3. Review contract terms
4. Use digital signature tool
5. Confirm signature
6. Contract is signed, project status updates

### How to Make Payment

1. Go to project with active phases
2. View phase details
3. Tap "Pay" button on unpaid phase
4. Enter payment details
5. Confirm payment
6. Phase becomes available for completion by service provider

### How to Complete a Phase (Service Provider)

1. Go to assigned project
2. View phase details
3. Ensure payment has been received (check payment status)
4. Complete work for the phase
5. Tap "Complete Phase" button (only visible if payment received)
6. Phase status updates to "Completed"

### How to Create Portfolio (Service Provider)

1. Go to Home tab
2. Tap "Create Portfolio" button (purple button above Available Projects)
3. Read benefits and information
4. Tap "Create Portfolio"
5. Fill out form:
   - Enter bio/description
   - Select years of experience
   - Upload certificates (photos)
   - Select service regions
6. Tap "Submit"
7. Wait for admin approval
8. Once approved, portfolio becomes public

### How to Submit a Bid (Service Provider)

1. Go to Projects tab or Home → Available Projects
2. Browse available projects
3. Tap on a project to view details
4. Review project requirements and phases
5. Tap "Bid Now" button
6. Fill bid form:
   - Enter price for each phase
   - Set total project price
   - Estimate duration
   - Add notes (optional)
7. Tap "Submit Bid"
8. Bid status: Pending → Accepted/Rejected

### How to Change Language

1. Go to Profile tab
2. Scroll to Settings section
3. Tap "Language" option
4. Toggle between Arabic (AR) and English (EN)
5. App language changes immediately

### How to Change Font Size

1. Go to Profile tab
2. Scroll to Settings section
3. Tap "Font Size" option
4. Select from menu:
   - *Small*: 90% of base size
   - *Medium*: 100% of base size (default)
   - *Large*: 140% of base size
5. Font size updates throughout app immediately

### How to Toggle Dark Mode

1. Go to Profile tab
2. Scroll to Settings section
3. Find "Dark Mode" option
4. Toggle switch On/Off
5. App theme changes immediately

---

## Settings and Preferences

### Profile Tab Settings

*Location*: Profile tab → Settings section

*Available Settings*:
1. *Language*: Switch between Arabic and English
2. *Dark Mode*: Toggle light/dark theme
3. *User Mode*: Toggle between Normal and Advanced mode
4. *Font Size*: Small, Medium, or Large
5. *Support Center*: Access help and support tickets

### Profile Information

*Location*: Profile tab → My Info card

*Shows*:
- Account status
- Email address
- Phone number
- User role (User or Service Provider)

### Statistics

*Location*: Profile tab → Statistics buttons

*Buttons*:
- *Properties*: Number of properties (users)
- *Appointments*: Number of appointments
- *Tickets*: Support tickets count

### My Portfolio (Service Providers Only)

*Location*: Profile tab → My Portfolio section

*Features*:
- View portfolio status
- Navigate to Portfolio Management
- Generate PDF portfolio
- Manage past projects

### My Subscriptions (Service Providers Only)

*Location*: Profile tab → My Subscriptions section

*Features*:
- View active subscriptions
- Manage subscription plans
- Renew subscriptions

---

## Navigation Structure

### User Navigation Flow


Splash Screen
    ↓
Login/Signup
    ↓
HomeView (User)
    ├── Service Providers (horizontal scroll)
    ├── My Projects List
    ├── Search Bar
    └── Tab Bar
        ├── Profile
        ├── New Project (+)
        ├── Home
        ├── My Projects
        └── Appointments

My Projects Tab
    ├── Filter: All/Pending/Active/Completed
    └── Project Cards (2-column grid)
        └── Tap → ProjectStatusTimelineView

Appointments Tab
    ├── Calendar Widget
    ├── Filter: Today/Pending/Upcoming/Completed
    └── Appointment Cards

Profile Tab
    ├── Welcome Card
    ├── My Info Card
    ├── Statistics Buttons
    ├── My Portfolio (if technician)
    ├── My Subscriptions (if technician)
    └── Settings
        ├── Language
        ├── Dark Mode
        ├── User Mode
        ├── Font Size
        └── Support Center


### Service Provider Navigation Flow


Splash Screen
    ↓
Login/Signup
    ↓
Complete Profile (if first time)
    ↓
Waiting for Approval (if pending)
    ↓
HomeService (Service Provider)
    ├── Create Portfolio Button
    ├── Available Projects
    ├── Assigned Projects
    └── Action Buttons (2x2 grid)
        ├── Look for Offers
        ├── Direct Offers
        ├── My Offers
        └── Bidded Projects

Projects Tab
    └── AvailableProjectsView
        └── All available projects (2-column grid)

Appointments Tab
    └── AppointmentsListView

Payments Tab
    └── CommissionPaymentView

Profile Tab
    └── Same as user profile


