## Project Creation Flow

### AI-Assisted Project Creation

1. *Start*: Home tab → "+" button → "Using AI"
2. *Conversational AI Form*:
   - Describe project in natural language
   - AI asks clarifying questions
   - AI generates project details
3. *Review AI Suggestions*:
   - Project title and description
   - Category
   - Phases
   - Budget estimates
   - Duration estimates
4. *Edit if Needed*: Modify any AI-generated content
5. *Add Details*:
   - Address/location
   - Upload photos
6. *Submit*: Create project
7. *Result*: Project appears in "My Projects" with "Pending" status

### Manual Project Creation

1. *Start*: Home tab → "+" button → "Manually"
2. *Fill Project Form*:
   - Project title
   - Description
   - Category selection
   - Address (required)
   - Budget (total)
   - Duration (estimated)
3. *Add Phases*:
   - Tap "Add Phase"
   - Enter phase name
   - Set phase budget
   - Set phase duration
   - Repeat for multiple phases
4. *Upload Photos*: Add project images
5. *Submit*: Create project
6. *Result*: Project created, status: "Pending"

---

## Project Status Flow

### User Project Statuses

1. *Creating*: Project being created
2. *Pending*: Waiting for service provider bids
3. *Bid Received*: Bids available for review
4. *Approved*: Bid accepted, contract ready
5. *Contract*: Contract signed, work in progress
6. *Active*: Project phases being executed
7. *Completed*: All phases finished

### Phase Status Flow

1. *Pending*: Phase not started
2. *In Progress*: Work being done
3. *Payment Required*: Phase completed, awaiting payment
4. *Paid*: Payment received, can be completed
5. *Completed*: Phase finished and approved

---

## Bidding Process

### For Service Providers

1. *Browse Projects*: Projects tab or Home → Available Projects
2. *View Project Details*: Tap project card
3. *Review Requirements*:
   - Project description
   - Phases and requirements
   - Budget range
   - Location
4. *Submit Bid*:
   - Enter price per phase
   - Set total price
   - Estimate duration
   - Add notes
5. *Wait for Response*: Bid status: Pending
6. *Outcome*:
   - *Accepted*: Project assigned, status changes
   - *Rejected*: Bid not selected

### For Users

1. *Receive Bids*: Project status changes to "Bid Received"
2. *View Bids*: Open project, see all submitted bids
3. *Compare Bids*: Review prices, durations, notes
4. *Accept Bid*: Tap "Accept" on preferred bid
5. *Result*: Project status → "Approved", contract available

---

## Contract and Payment Flow

### Contract Signing

1. *Project Status*: Must be "Approved"
2. *Access Contract*: Tap "Sign Contract" in project view
3. *Review Terms*: Read contract details
4. *Sign*: Use digital signature tool
5. *Confirm*: Submit signature
6. *Result*: Contract signed, project status → "Contract"

### Phase Payment

1. *Project Status*: Must be "Contract" or "Active"
2. *View Phases*: Open project, see phase list
3. *Check Phase Status*: Find phase marked "Payment Required"
4. *Pay Phase*: Tap "Pay" button
5. *Enter Payment Details*: Complete payment form
6. *Confirm Payment*: Submit payment
7. *Result*: Phase status → "Paid", service provider can complete

### Phase Completion (Service Provider)

1. *Check Payment*: Ensure phase is marked "Paid"
2. *Complete Work*: Finish phase requirements
3. *Submit Completion*: Tap "Complete Phase" button
4. *Result*: Phase status → "Completed"

*Important*: "Complete Phase" button only appears if payment received

---

## Appointment Management

### Booking Appointment (User)

1. *Find Service Provider*: Browse services or search
2. *View Provider Profile*: Tap service provider
3. *Book Appointment*: Tap "Book Appointment"
4. *Select Date*: Use calendar picker
5. *Select Time*: Choose available time slot
6. *Add Details*: Project description (optional)
7. *Confirm*: Submit appointment request
8. *Result*: Appointment appears in "Appointments" tab

### Managing Appointments

*Location*: Appointments tab

*Features*:
- *Calendar*: View and select dates
- *Filters*:
  - *Today*: Today's appointments
  - *Pending*: Awaiting confirmation
  - *Upcoming*: Future appointments
  - *Completed*: Past appointments
- *Appointment Card Shows*:
  - Project/service description
  - Date and time
  - Address/location
  - Status badge
  - Total amount (if applicable)

*Actions*:
- View appointment details
- Reschedule appointment
- Cancel appointment
- Mark as completed (service providers)

---

## Portfolio Management (Service Providers)

### Creating Portfolio

1. *Access*: Home tab → "Create Portfolio" button
2. *View Information*: Read benefits and instructions
3. *Start Creation*: Tap "Create Portfolio"
4. *Fill Form*:
   - *Bio*: Professional description
   - *Years of Experience*: Select from picker
   - *Certificates*: Upload photos of certificates
   - *Regions*: Select service areas (can select all)
5. *Submit*: Tap "Submit"
6. *Wait for Approval*: Status: "Waiting for Approval"
7. *After Approval*: Portfolio becomes public

### Managing Portfolio

*Location*: Profile tab → My Portfolio

*Features*:
- *Generate PDF*: Create downloadable portfolio PDF
- *Download PDF*: Save PDF to device
- *QR Code*: Generate QR code for portfolio sharing
- *Past Projects*: Add, edit, delete past project entries
- *Edit Portfolio*: Update bio, experience, certificates, regions

### Adding Past Projects

1. *Access*: Profile → My Portfolio → Past Projects
2. *Add Project*: Tap "Add Past Project"
3. *Fill Form*:
   - Project title
   - Description
   - Category
   - Completion date
   - Upload photos
4. *Save*: Submit project
5. *Result*: Project appears in portfolio

