## Notifications

### Notification Types

1. *Project Updates*: Status changes, new bids
2. *Appointment Reminders*: Upcoming appointments
3. *Bid Responses*: Bid accepted/rejected
4. *Contract Updates*: Contract ready, signed
5. *Payment Notifications*: Payment received, required
6. *Chat Messages*: New messages from users/providers

### Notification Access

*Location*: Header → Notification bell icon (top right)

*Features*:
- Badge shows unread count
- List of all notifications
- Filter by type
- Mark as read
- Tap to navigate to related content

