## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

#### Project Not Appearing
- *Check*: My Projects tab
- *Filter*: Try "All" filter
- *Refresh*: Pull down to refresh
- *Status*: Check if project is in correct status filter

#### Cannot Complete Phase
- *Check Payment*: Phase must be paid first
- *Status*: Verify phase status is "Paid"
- *Button*: "Complete Phase" only appears after payment

#### Cannot Submit Bid
- *Check Project*: Ensure project is available
- *Status*: Project must be in "Pending" or "Bid Received" status
- *Form*: Ensure all required fields filled

#### Portfolio Not Approved
- *Check Status*: View "Waiting for Approval" page
- *Complete Data*: Ensure all required fields submitted
- *Contact Support*: Use Support Center if delayed

#### Font Size Not Changing
- *Check Setting*: Profile → Font Size
- *Refresh*: Navigate away and back
- *Restart*: Close and reopen app

#### Language Not Changing
- *Check Setting*: Profile → Language
- *Refresh*: Navigate to different tab and back
- *Restart App*: Close and reopen

#### Dark Mode Not Working
- *Check Setting*: Profile → Dark Mode toggle
- *System Setting*: Ensure device allows dark mode
- *Refresh*: Navigate away and back

---

