## Best Practices

### For Users
1. *Clear Project Descriptions*: Help service providers understand needs
2. *Upload Photos*: Visual references improve project understanding
3. *Review Bids Carefully*: Compare prices, durations, and notes
4. *Respond Promptly*: Accept/reject bids in timely manner
5. *Complete Payments*: Enable service providers to complete work
6. *Use Chat*: Communicate with service providers for clarifications

### For Service Providers
1. *Complete Profile*: Full profile increases credibility
2. *Create Portfolio*: Showcase past work
3. *Detailed Bids*: Provide clear pricing and timelines
4. *Respond Quickly*: Fast bid responses improve chances
5. *Update Status*: Keep project status current
6. *Professional Communication*: Use chat for clear communication

