## Quick Reference

### Navigation Shortcuts
- *Home*: Tap center circular button in tab bar
- *New Project*: Tap "+" button (left of center)
- *Profile*: Tap profile icon (left tab)
- *Projects*: Tap "My Projects" (right tab) or "Projects" (service providers)
- *Appointments*: Tap calendar icon (right tab)

### Common Actions
- *Search*: Tap search bar at top
- *Notifications*: Tap bell icon (top right)
- *Chat*: Tap chat bubble icon (top right) or floating chatbot button
- *Settings*: Profile tab → Settings section
- *Help*: Floating chatbot button or Support Center

